  Description: Assassin who has abandoned his name and covered his face. Behind that
    pall is a burning fanaticism and a destined fate.
  Skillset: "\u2022 [Feud Bonding] Greatly reduces damages taken, however this effect
    gradually wears off the longer the current player stays on the field.\n\n<b>FIRST
    PHASE</b>\n\n\u2022 [Pack Up] When faraway from the player, charges up and quickly
    dash toward their position, dealing physical damage to the player if comes into
    contact with.\n\u2022 [Held Breath] When [Feud Bonding] effects wear off, slows
    the current player for several seconds.\n\n<b>SECOND PHASE</b>\n\n\u2022 [Toward
    Death] Stop moving, then creates multiple illusion of self. After a short delay,
    dashes toward these illusions in quick succession and damages the player if coming
    into contact with them."
